stories.title: South Africa coast to seven-wicket victory over Kenya
stories.summary: South Africa barely raised a sweat at Willowmoore Park in Benoni on Sunday, coasting to a seven-wicket win over Kenya in the second match of the Standard Bank triangular one-day series
